Subject: [PATCH] Lintfix

---
 salt/roster/__init__.py | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/salt/roster/__init__.py b/salt/roster/__init__.py
index aa4dd335c83b..9ec700b947fb 100644
